ActCanadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission Act
PrecisAppointment of PETER MENZIES of Calgary, Alberta, to be a full-time member of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; designate PETER MENZIES to be Vice-Chairperson of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission.
